<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="41" type="remark">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="41">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="41">
<bibRefCitation author="Pang, XF" journalOrPublisher="Science Press, China, Beijing" pageId="12" pageNumber="47" title="Coleoptera: Coccinellidae II. Economic Entomology China" year="1979">Pang and Mao (1979)</bibRefCitation>
transferred 
<taxonomicName authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afissa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afissa siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afissa siamensis</taxonomicName>
Dieke into 
<taxonomicName authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidenta</taxonomicName>
without any explanation. However, a detailed examination of 
<taxonomicName authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afidenta siamensis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta misera" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="misera">Afidenta misera</taxonomicName>
left no doubt that they do not belong to a same genus, and that diagnostic characters of 
<taxonomicName authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afidenta siamensis</taxonomicName>
match 
<taxonomicName authority="Kapur, 1955" authorityName="Kapur" authorityYear="1955" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidentula" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidentula" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidentula</taxonomicName>
. Thus this species in formally transfered to the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Kapur, 1955" authorityName="Kapur" authorityYear="1955" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidentula" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidentula" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidentula</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
